    "index_reference": "48001001-48001010",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108102\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">保羅</span>非常關心<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108077\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">加拉太</span>的<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108122\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">信徒</span>，他們相信保羅教導他們的關於<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108043\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">耶穌</span>的<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108219\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">好消息</span>。但是保羅離開後，其他教師來到了加拉太，他們教導的內容與關於耶穌的好消息相違背，加拉太人也開始相信那些教導。於是再次<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108199\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">神</span>派保羅去傳講好消息，這是保羅作<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108208\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">使徒</span>的<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108053\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">工作</span>本分。保羅對他所傳講的真理的信息有完全的確信，他傳講耶穌為<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108195\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">人類</span>的<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108202\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">罪</span>捨命。耶穌使那些<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108255\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">信</span>祂的人從這個邪惡的<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108215\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">世界</span>中得自由，這是保羅描述罪、死亡和邪惡的權勢的方式。<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108312\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">父</span>希望耶穌使人得自由，因此，所有關於耶穌的教導必須與此一致。如果不一致，耶穌的跟隨者必須拒絕相信。</p>",
